    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>One cool feature we could add to Zend form is a password stength verificator ; it could use a little dojo / ajax to work (so it might concern only Zend_Dojo_Forms, but it's a nice feature on login forms.</p>

<p>This is a fairly commun feature on subscription forms : one progress bar that tells the strength of the password : weak/medium/strong.
This feature could work with points : 
1 point per character used ; with minimal password length
3 points per upper character
5 points per special character ;</p>

<p>Weak : under 4 points ; medium 5 points ; strong  ; 12 points, etc.</p>

